---
title: Jumbo Coconut Shrimp Platter with Coleslaw and Potato Wedges
description: Prepare to feast on this scrumptious coconut jumbo shrimp platter! Succulent shrimp is coated in a crunchy panko-coconut breading, then shallow-fried to perfection. Paired with a creamy coleslaw, roasted potato wedges and a spicy mango sauce, this feast will transport you to flavour paradise!
